      "report_preview": "## 1. Executive Summary\nCrowdWisdomTrading (CWT) distinguishes itself in the crowded trading signals market by aggregating insights from over 2,086 professional traders into AI-powered weekly signals with a 73.3% success rate, targeting time-constrained retail traders. While facing stiff competition from prediction markets like Kalshi and Polymarket, social platforms like eToro and TradingView, and AI signal providers like Trade Ideas, CWT's focus on actionable trade entries, stop-losses, and targets provides a unique edge in collective intelligence. Strategic emphasis on verified performance tracking and time savings positions CWT for growth amid a booming prediction and social trading sector.\n\n## 2. Market Overview\nThe trading signals and prediction markets sector is experiencing rapid expansion, driven by retail trader adoption of social and crowd-sourced intelligence, with prediction markets alone seeing tens of millions of users amid a \"gold rush\" from entrants like Coinbase and R",
